snippet.title: EXCLUSIVE - Watch Amber Heard Gush About France's World Cup Victory At LAX!
snippet.description:
Monday, July 16, 2018 - Amber Heard flaunts her taut tummy in a black midriff polo top, paired with blue Levi's, wearing a black hat and sunglasses as she arrives in Los Angeles. The 'Aquaman' star is all smiles amid her budding romance with Vito Schnabel, stopping to greet fans and sign autographs as she makes her way to her car. When asked if she's happy for France after their World Cup victory yesterday, Heard responds, "Yes I am, it was fun to watch."
